{"tid":1414983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[好重要]請勇武手足隨身帶索帶！","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T12:05:33.000Z","uid":73855,"like":86,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"31f5b237f096d29f2e2332c84920b3f673dc5a5f","tid":1414983,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:04:13.000Z","msg":"愈嚟愈多白衫佬、便衣警員會混入人群搞事、撩人隻抽。喺哩個時候，「自衛」就一撚定，但請記得以制伏為前題，唔係洩憤。今日睇戲見到打到個攞棍嘅無反應，要first aid，畫面真係幾趕客，尤其對老一輩或者淺黃。<br />\n<br />\n你一個人同佢隻抽就梗係冇乜所謂啦，但手足一湧而上抽水，就好難控制到佢會唔會畀人打死，一人一拳，又或者一人一棍就真係可能死人。無錯，我想佢死，但我唔係想殺咗佢。<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有人死，運動可能被瓦解，大局為重。</span><br />\n<br />\n我哋唔可以殺人，但可以制伏，然後羞辱佢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">人多抽兩下水就㩒低佢，再用索帶索起佢，影下相、拍下片，想點玩都得啦。</span><br />\n<br />\n切記！制伏為主、攻擊為副。制伏、索起、羞辱，就係咁簡單。"},{"pid":"891dfa02561249fbffd0059697fb9189b15dec61","tid":1414983,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"b70e1663125c9b2f04145ccf17012cfbbdc823ce","tid":1414983,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:05:29.000Z","msg":"要"},{"pid":"6e060cae8d80479afd7e69c4d70cc945f67701b9","tid":1414983,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:05:39.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"e772199b7c1cdb17978c0eb535b24eda3ab15c37","tid":1414983,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"普"},{"pid":"383efda360895922c7a2ea1a98a42fa8c57b1df1","tid":1414983,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:06:02.000Z","msg":"選"},{"pid":"0d37b2236fc8210167416136cf51994543efec1f","tid":1414983,"uid":176166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"674479c7d72d642909fb284feb67f76a21b6515b","tid":1414983,"uid":73855,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"0d37b2236fc8210167416136cf51994543efec1f","tid":1414983,"uid":1761