3e5f74e01694e128dc8147f870200ba","tid":1414983,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:20:24.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"8248600c89c46d7697eefe78032bcd22813a88c1","tid":1414983,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:20:34.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"670e4dd4925ce1aa64f5d8a951256cd20a8d8466","tid":1414983,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:21:04.000Z","msg":"十連！睇嚟冇人認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca290fb8f19a899c396c39f71fd5c30078a94496","tid":1414983,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:24:50.000Z","msg":"［有片］北角勇士擊退黑社會，好波！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1414847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1414847</a><br />\n<br />\n一睇再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1dfed3e8745044ef2381eeafdbffdf3ed4bf9f8","tid":1414983,"uid":73855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:25:36.000Z","msg":"多倫多大學政治科學系助理教授 Lynette H. Ong 的論文「惡煞僱傭﹕中國的國家高壓管治與『日常鎮壓』(&ldquo;Thugs-for-Hire&rdquo;: State Coercion and &ldquo;Everyday Repression&rdquo; in China)」。（下文為《立場新聞》中文撮要）<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n中國國家經常動用第三方暴力（如黑社會）打擊示威者與請願者。「暴力對實踐不受歡迎及違法的政策十分有效用、有效率。」因為這方式可以令國家逃避責任，維持合法性。然而這種形式亦有其代價﹕國家體制的合法性及人民對國家的信任，勢必受損。她說，借用暴力的管治手法只能支撐體制的專制統治，對強化其管治基礎毫無幫助。"},{"pid":"b2d30a8e6842f21a9a6b98ef3b3b9a0e3932e96a","tid":1414983,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:26:21.000Z","msg":"我係黃大仙走埋去淋熄啲火個條女，我有嘢想講。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415093</a><br />\n<br />\n黃大仙紀律部隊宿舍裡面有黑警，但都有消防、有救護等等其他紀律部隊，有同路人亦都有英雄。"},{"pid":"674b6967a40899c8fbad4c6add142fad8e578a81","tid":1414983,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-0